        },
        "faq_item_WLYpJt": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "tab_id": "medications",
            "question": "Can Berkeley Life be taken with blood pressure or ED medications?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes. Berkeley Life is safe and well-tolerated with no known contraindications. However, we recommend speaking with your healthcare provider to ensure the right combination of medication and supplementation.</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_Jq8UMr": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "tab_id": "medications",
            "question": "Are there any contraindication to using Berkeley Life?",
            "answer": "<p>There are no known contraindications or reported adverse events. A good rule of thumb: if you can eat a leafy green salad, you can take Berkeley Life.</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_ALFx3G": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "tab_id": "medications",
            "question": "Is it safe for people with oxalate sensitivities?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes. The oxalate content is extremely low—less than a single spinach leaf. Even individuals with sensitivities generally tolerate it well.</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_eahpwT": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "tab_id": "medications",
            "question": "Should I talk to my healthcare provider before starting Berkeley Life?",
            "answer": "<p>Berkeley Life NO Foundation is a dietary supplement that does not require a prescription. It’s formulated with plant-based nitrates to help support healthy nitric oxide levels, circulation, and cardiovascular wellness. It is safe for most adults to take it as part of their daily routine.</p><p>However, because it naturally supports blood pressure and circulation, it is recommended to consult your healthcare provider before starting, especially if you are pregnant, nursing, have a medical condition, or take prescription medications (such as for blood pressure or sexual function).<br/><br/></p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_xcBFPr": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "tab_id": "safety",
            "question": "Is Berkeley Life safe for daily use?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes. Berkeley Life is manufactured in the United States under FDA-registered, GMP-certified facilities, and undergoes rigorous internal and third-party testing to ensure safety and potency.</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_DeG7X4": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "tab_id": "safety",
            "question": "What quality standards do you follow?",
            "answer": "<p>Every ingredient is tested for identity, potency, and microbiological safety before use. Finished products undergo comprehensive quality checks and third-party testing before being released.</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_QctQnH": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "tab_id": "safety",
            "question": "Can I validate that Berkeley Life is working for me?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes. You can use the Nitric Oxide Test Strips before and 90 minutes after taking the supplement to confirm effectiveness.</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_QjPgkr": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "tab_id": "safety",
            "question": "Where is Berkeley Life made?",
            "answer": "<p>Supplements are manufactured in the USA, and test strips are produced in Europe.</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_aNRGdk": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "tab_id": "dosage",
            "question": "How much should I take daily?",
            "answer": "<p>Take two capsules daily with water, preferably after a meal.</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_gCKxeV": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "tab_id": "dosage",
            "question": "How long do I need to take Berkeley Life before I see results?",
            "answer": "<p>Results vary, some notice a difference right away, while others see benefits after about a month. Consistency is key, and test strips can validate improvements quickly.</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_KAmrV7": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "tab_id": "dosage",
            "question": "How long should I continue taking Nitric Oxide support?",
            "answer": "<p>Since natural nitric oxide production declines with age, ongoing daily support through diet or supplementation is recommended.</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_CCyhPB": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "tab_id": "dosage",
            "question": "What if my test strip doesn’t change color?",
            "answer": "<p>If you recently ate or drank, saliva may be diluted, causing a false negative. In rare cases, low oral bacteria levels may impact conversion. We recommend discussing ways to support your oral microbiome with your healthcare provider.</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_JXpr3L": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "tab_id": "shipping",
            "question": "How long will it take to get my order?",
            "answer": "<p>Orders placed before 2 PM EST ship the same day and typically arrive in 3–7 business days within the US. Canadian orders may take 7–16 days.</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_xBjmM8": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "tab_id": "shipping",
            "question": "Do you ship internationally?",
            "answer": "<p>We currently ship to the US and Canada. Customers in the UK and Europe can purchase Berkeley Life through our trusted partner, Healf.</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        },
        "faq_item_zXJCWh": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "tab_id": "shipping",
            "question": "How do I manage my subscription?",
            "answer": "<p>You can manage your subscription by logging into your account. If you have trouble, contact help@berkeleylife.com or call 844-517-1327 (Mon–Fri, 9 AM–5 PM EST).</p>",
            "open_by_default": false
          }
        }
      },
